data.description: *** PRICE IMPROVEMENT!  ** Residential Lease in place until January 31st, 2024.  Almost brand new, great new home neighborhood, close to Hill AFB, Clinton shopping center.  Beautiful corner lot with a spacious open concept kitchen with island, quartz countertops, 9' ceilings, and plenty of 42" tall cabinetry.  Large Walk in closet, extra large upstairs loft, and 8' garage door.   * $45,000 SOLAR INCLUDED and paid at closing w/23 year warranty!    Closing around February 1st is ideal.
